  "name": "Breacher Squad",
  "titles": "Breacher Squad",
  "lore": "The most hazardous spheres of warfare such as boarding actions and the first wave of attackers into a breached fortress domain can prove lethal beyond endurance, even for the warriors of the Legiones Astartes. For this reason, since the early days of the Great Crusade, specialised wargear and tactics have been under continuous development including the use of heavy ablative shields to resist enemy fire and specialised weaponry to bypass bulkheads and shatter strongpoints. Breacher squads are the fruit of this development, with all Legions utilising them across many theatres of war.",
